Otyebis Staff:




Thirty armed soldiers came outside of the Otyebis to meet with Dark Pika, 
Obsidian, Pika-Hawk, Noble, Penguin, Dark Penguin, Dark Pika, Dark Rat, 
Bruiser, and Penguin 2.

"Follow us." the leader of the IGL soldiers said, the thiry men entering the 
Otyebis through a hatch.
